#: ../../doc/start.rst:2
msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前置要求"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:4
msgid "AngelScript 2.37.0 or newer."
msgstr "AngelScript 2.37.0 或更新版本。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:5
msgid ""
"Any C++ compiler that supports C++20 features required by this library. "
"This library mainly depends on ``requires`` and ``<concepts>`` from "
"C++20."
msgstr ""
"任意支持本库所需的 C++20 特性的 C++ 编译器。"
"本库主要依赖 C++20 的 ``requires`` 和 ``<concepts>``。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:8
msgid ""
"If the compiler and standard library support newer features like C++23, "
"asbind20 will enable support for them."
msgstr ""
"如果编译器和标准库支持 C++23 等更新的特性，"
"asbind20 将启用对这些特性的支持。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:11
msgid ""
"There is a nightly build script in CI of asbind20, testing its "
"compatibility with `the latest WIP version of AngelScript "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/wip.php>`_. If you are using a WIP"
" version of AS for newest features or fixes, you need to consider using "
"the latest release of asbind20, or even the development branch."
msgstr ""
"asbind20 的 CI 中有一个每日构建脚本，用于测试其与"
"`最新的 AngelScript WIP 版本 <https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/wip.php>`_ 的兼容性。"
"如果你使用 AS 的 WIP 版本以获得最新功能或修复，"
"需要考虑使用 asbind20 的最新发布版本，甚至是开发分支。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:18
msgid "Supported Platforms"
msgstr "支持的平台"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:20
msgid ""
"Currently, the following platforms and compilers are officially supported"
" and `tested by CI "
"<https://github.com/HenryAWE/asbind20/blob/master/.github/workflows/build.yml>`_."
" However, asbind20 on other platforms, architectures or compiler "
"toolchains supported by AngelScript should work as expected too."
msgstr ""
"目前，以下平台和编译器受到官方支持并"
"`通过 CI 进行测试 <https://github.com/HenryAWE/asbind20/blob/master/.github/workflows/build.yml>`_。"
"不过，asbind20 在 AngelScript 支持的其他平台、架构或编译器工具链上也应该能够正常工作。"

