#: ../../doc/start.rst:50
msgid ""
"The \"latest\" or \"latest-stable\" in the above table mean the (stable) "
"latest version of compiler toolchain available in CI when asbind20 "
"releases a new stable version. You can check the release date of "
"historical versions in the :doc:`changelog`."
msgstr ""
"上表中 \"latest\" 或 \"latest-stable\" 指的是 asbind20 发布新稳定版本时 CI 中可用的"
"（稳定）最新版本的编译器工具链。"
"你可以查看 :doc:`changelog` 中历史版本的发布日期。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:53
msgid ""
"Newer Clang toolchains (like Clang 18+) support both libstdc++ and "
"libc++, while the older toolchains (like Clang 15) on libstdc++ are not "
"guaranteed to work as expected."
msgstr ""
"较新的 Clang 工具链（如 Clang 18+）同时支持 libstdc++ 和 libc++，"
"而较旧的工具链（如 Clang 15）在 libstdc++ 上的运行则不能保证完全正常。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:56
msgid ""
"Additionally, the Clang 18 toolchain on x64 Linux is tested for compiling"
" with address sanitizer and ``AS_USE_NAMESPACE`` enabled."
msgstr ""
"此外，x64 Linux 上的 Clang 18 工具链还通过了启用地址消毒器和 ``AS_USE_NAMESPACE`` 的编译测试。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:59
msgid ""
"This library on older compiler toolchains, like GCC 12, still works as "
"expected under most situations, but it might need some workarounds to "
"deal with defects of the compiler, e.g., additional ``typename`` in "
"template-related code. Please use newer compiler toolchains if possible."
msgstr ""
"本库在较旧的编译器工具链（如 GCC 12）上在大多数情况下仍能正常工作，"
"但可能需要一些变通方法来处理编译器的缺陷，"
"例如在模板相关代码中额外添加 ``typename``。"
"请尽可能使用较新的编译器工具链。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:64
msgid "Integrate into Your Project"
msgstr "集成到你的项目中"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:66
msgid ""
"Please follow the `tutorial of AngelScript to build and install it "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_compile_lib.html>`_"
" at first, or use a package manager like `vcpkg "
"<https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg>`_."
msgstr ""
"请先参考 `AngelScript 的教程来构建和安装它 "
"<https://www.angelcode.com/angelscript/sdk/docs/manual/doc_compile_lib.html>`_，"
"或使用 `vcpkg <https://github.com/microsoft/vcpkg>`_ 等包管理器。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:69
msgid ""
"Besides, if your project has a custom location of ``<angelscript.h>``, "
"you can include it before any asbind20 headers. This library will not "
"include the AngelScript library for the second time by detecting the "
"macro ``ANGELSCRIPT_H``."
msgstr ""
"此外，如果你的项目有自定义的 ``<angelscript.h>`` 路径，"
"可以在包含任何 asbind20 头文件之前先包含它。"
"本库会通过检测宏 ``ANGELSCRIPT_H`` 来避免重复包含 AngelScript 库。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:73
msgid "1. Copy into Your Project"
msgstr "1. 复制到你的项目中"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:75
msgid ""
"This is a header-only library. You can directly copy all the files under "
"``include/`` into your project, then set a correct include directory for "
"your project."
msgstr ""
"这是一个仅头文件库。"
"你可以直接将 ``include/`` 下的所有文件复制到你的项目中，"
"然后为你的项目设置正确的包含目录。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:80
msgid "2. Integration Using CMake"
msgstr "2. 使用 CMake 集成"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:82
msgid "CMake 3.20 or newer is required."
msgstr "需要 CMake 3.20 或更新版本。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:85
msgid "A. Submodule"
msgstr "A. 子模块"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:87
msgid ""
"You can add asbind20 through git submodule and then use "
"``add_subdirectory``."
msgstr ""
"你可以通过 git 子模块添加 asbind20，然后使用 ``add_subdirectory``。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:96
msgid "B. Build and Install"
msgstr "B. 构建并安装"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:98
msgid "Additionally, you can install and link against asbind20 using CMake."
msgstr "此外，你可以使用 CMake 安装和链接 asbind20。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:105
msgid "Then, link the library in a ``CMakeLists.txt``."
msgstr "然后在 ``CMakeLists.txt`` 中链接该库。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:114
msgid "1. Integration with XMake Projects"
msgstr "1. 与 XMake 项目集成"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:116
msgid ""
"Since the version 1.6.0, asbind20 has been accepted into the `official "
"package registry (xmake-repo) <https://github.com/xmake-io/xmake-repo>`_."
" You can easily add asbind20 as a dependency of your project."
msgstr ""
"自 1.6.0 版本起，asbind20 已被收录到"
"`官方包注册表 (xmake-repo) <https://github.com/xmake-io/xmake-repo>`_ 中。"
"你可以轻松地将 asbind20 添加为项目的依赖项。"

#: ../../doc/start.rst:127
msgid ""
"Please check the `official documentation of XMake about adding packages "
"<https://xmake.io/guide/project-configuration/add-packages.html>`_ for "
"more details."
msgstr ""
"更多详情请查阅 `XMake 关于添加包的官方文档 "
"<https://xmake.io/guide/project-configuration/add-packages.html>`_。"

